reviewText:
Super fast party game!
You are kitty that tries to rise to the top!

Use your psychic powers to do damage in another kitty

Game modes:
Coins (Try to steal coins from another kitty)
Bread (Be Bread in last second)
Brawl (Kill another kitty)
Pros
Fast pace
Great Kawaii(Asian) visual style
Ability to customize your own kitty
Challenging controls (get used to)
Good amount of different stages
No bugs
Cons
Only 3 game modes
Suggestions

Mutators! (Super big kitty, Super bouncy kitty etc.)
More game modes
Drop some powerups in levels
Conclusion

Right now this is pretty funny fast pace party game with few game modes!
